{"tid":2016842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【利字當頭】沒有救海洋公園的理由 - 利世民","createTime":"2020-05-14T16:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T16:50:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e2917fb533d54b4ea4405370508dbbf37bd6bb","tid":2016842,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200514/33Z6HGDLQFMTLOHJ4KC2S4BKMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200514%2F33Z6HGDLQFMTLOHJ4KC2S4BKMI%2F&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7oL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=1f776b28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200514%2F33Z6HGDLQFMTLOHJ4KC2S4BKMI%2F&h=98216624\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200514/33Z6HGDLQFMTLOHJ4KC2S4BKMI/</a><br />\n<br />\n【利字當頭】沒有救海洋公園的理由 - 利世民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200514/large/1589387619_4cc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200514%2Flarge%2F1589387619_4cc7.jpg&h=63ed7b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實大多數香港人都冇幫襯海洋公園，咁點解用香港納稅人嘅錢去救？資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n「有冇。。。。。。。。。。。。。。去救？<br />\n<br />\n「多人去，就唔使救啦！」Bingo，咁點解冇人去，就值得救？即係我一世人都係去過幾次福臨門，咁假如有日富豪飯堂要搵人打救，冇理由要我科水，係咪？至於咩集體回憶之類嘅論點，我奉勸有關當局都係唔好吹奏太多。<br />\n<br />\n執笠，。。。。。。<br />\n。。。。。。。Out喇。<br />\n<br />\n市場係咁殘酷，但係焗香港人去救海洋公園，直頭係不公不義。派錢畀多數人，尚且都可以話係還富於民；救海洋公園？我第一個問題係，點解班管理層又唔需要問責？<br />\n<br />\n話說。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。要救。<br />\n<br />\n利世民<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/leesimon.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fleesimon.hk&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7oL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=b30a8c07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/leesimon.hk</a><br />\n本欄逢周二、四刊出"}]}